  "description": "<p>分类: <a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/category/transportation/\" rel=\"tag\">交通相关</a>, <a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/category/wearables/\" rel=\"tag\">佩戴产品</a></p><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2013/10/08/google-glass-now-offers-mass-transit-directions/\"><img src=\"http://www.blogcdn.com/cn.engadget.com/media/2013/10/google-glass-mass-transit.jpg\" style=\"margin: 4px;\" /></a></div>\n\n<div><br />\n步行指向对 <a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/tag/googleglass\">Google Glass</a> 的使用者来说已经不是什么新鲜玩意了，而在今天早些时候上线的更新中，Google 又为其加入了公共交通指向的功能。现在用户在查询出行方向时，只需将 Google Glass 与 Android 手机配对，之后就能看到与目的地间相隔的站点、预计到达时间等信息了。对常搭乘公共交通的 Google Glass 佩带者来说这无疑是非常实用的一次更新，<a href=\"http://techcrunch.com/2013/01/21/sergey-brin-dons-google-glass-dresses-like-an-international-jewel-thief-for-nyc-subway-ride/\">Sergey Brin</a>，你同意吗？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n经由：<a href=\"http://www.engadget.com/2013/10/07/google-glass-now-offers-mass-transit-directions/\">Engadget</a><br />\n引用来源：<a href=\"https://plus.google.com/u/0/+GoogleGlass/posts/VrkuxM7uLc7\" target=\"_blank\">Google Glass (Google+)</a></div><p><h6 style=\"clear: both; padding: 8px 0 0 0; height: 2px; font-size: 1px; border: 0; margin: 0; padding: 0;\"></h6><a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2013/10/08/google-glass-now-offers-mass-transit-directions/\" rel=\"bookmark\" title=\"Permanent link to this entry\">此文章网址</a>&nbsp;|&nbsp;<a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/forward/20740062/\" title=\"Send this entry to a friend via email\">转寄此文章</a>&nbsp;|&nbsp;<a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2013/10/08/google-glass-now-offers-mass-transit-directions/#comments\" title=\"View reader comments on this entry\">回应</a><hr size=\"1\" />", 
